                    LUMEN BOT - PRIVACY POLICY
================================================================================

Last updated: March 3, 2026

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. INTRODUCTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lumen Colors ("we," "us," "our") operates the Lumen Discord bot ("Bot"). This
Privacy Policy explains what data the Bot collects, how we use it, and your
rights regarding that data. By using the Bot, you agree to this policy.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. DATA WE COLLECT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Bot stores the following data to provide its services:

  (a) Server (guild) configuration
      When a server uses the Bot (e.g., after running the setup command), we
      store configuration data associated with that server's Discord guild ID,
      including:
      - Channel ID where color-role messages are posted
      - Color set and role configuration (e.g., role names, emoji associations)
      - Message IDs and channel IDs of the Bot's embed messages
      - Optional: required role ID and restricted role ID (if the server
        administrator configures role restrictions)
      - Optional: custom banner image URLs per color family
      - The Discord user ID of the user who ran the setup command ("setupBy")
        for reference only

  (b) Guild addition records
      When the Bot is added to a server, we store the Discord guild ID and the
      Discord user ID of the user who added the Bot (the "inviter," typically
      the person who received the welcome DM). We use this solely to send that
      user a one-time welcome message with setup instructions and, in the
      future, to optionally notify them of important Bot updates (e.g., new
      features or critical changes). We do not sell or share this information
      with third parties for marketing or advertising.

  (c) Data we do not collect
      We do not collect or store:
      - Lists of all users who use color roles in a server
      - Message content from users (except when you explicitly send a role ID,
        emoji, or image/link during setup or dashboard flows; that data is used
        only to apply your chosen settings and is not used for profiling or
        advertising)
      - Any data for the purpose of advertising, selling to third parties, or
        building user profiles beyond what is necessary to operate the Bot

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. HOW WE USE THE DATA
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - To operate the Bot: We use server configuration and message/role data to
    display color-role menus, assign roles when users react, and allow
    administrators to edit settings via the dashboard.

  - Welcome and instructions: When you add the Bot to a server, we send a
    one-time direct message to the inviter with setup instructions.

  - Permission messages: If a user tries to use a color role but does not meet
    the server's requirements (e.g., missing required role or has restricted
    role), the Bot may send that user a one-time DM explaining why the action
    was not allowed.

  - Updates (optional): We may use the stored inviter user IDs to send
    important Bot update notifications (e.g., new features or breaking changes).
    We will not use this for promotional or marketing spam.

  - Legal and safety: We may retain or disclose data if required by law, to
    enforce our Terms of Service, or to protect the rights and safety of users
    or the public.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. DATA STORAGE AND RETENTION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - Data is stored in files on the Operator's infrastructure (e.g.,
    serverConfigs.json and guildAdditions.json). We do not use third-party
    analytics or advertising services that track users across the internet.

  - Server configuration is retained for as long as the Bot remains in the
    server and is used. If the Bot is removed from a server, we may remove that
    server's configuration data (e.g., when we detect the Bot is no longer in
    the guild).

  - Guild addition records (guild ID and inviter user ID) may be retained to
    allow future update notifications. If you are an inviter and do not wish to
    receive update messages, you may contact us at Discord: @aizy_lazy or Email: entertainmenthd23@gmail.com to request
    removal of your user ID from our records.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5. DISCORD AND THIRD PARTIES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - The Bot operates on Discord. Data we collect is processed through Discord's
    API and is subject to Discord's Privacy Policy and Terms of Service. We do
    not control Discord's practices.

  - We do not sell, rent, or trade your data to third parties for advertising
    or marketing. We do not use your data to build advertising profiles.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. DATA SECURITY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

We take reasonable measures to protect the data we store (e.g., access
controls and secure hosting). No method of transmission or storage is 100%
secure; we cannot guarantee absolute security.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7. YOUR RIGHTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:

  - Access the data we hold about you (e.g., your Discord user ID if stored as
    an inviter or setupBy);
  - Request correction or deletion of your data;
  - Object to or restrict certain processing;
  - Withdraw consent where processing is based on consent.

To exercise these rights or to ask questions about your data, contact us at
Discord: @aizy_lazy or Email: entertainmenthd23@gmail.com. We will respond within a reasonable time. If you are in the
European Economic Area or the United Kingdom, you may also have the right to
lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
